tourBios.exmtStatus: Conditional - Finished T93 at 2015 Web.com Tour Qualifying Tournament
tourBios.curYearHigh: Earned status with rounds of 74-72-69-68 at the Mackenzie Tour – PGA TOUR Canada Qualifying Tournament No.1.
tourBios.carHigh:
2015: Spent a majority of the year on the eGolf and Swing Thought Tours...Made two starts on the Mackenzie Tour and missed the cut in both events.

2014: Played in 16 events on the Web.com Tour with six made cuts...Lone top-25 finish was a T21 at the Stonebrae Classic.

2013: Made two starts on the Web.com Tour. Missed the cut at the Mid-Atlantic Championship and T41 at The Rex Hospital Open...Competed on eGolf Tour, winning the Founders Classic.
tourBios.otherCarHigh: Captured the 2008 and 2009 Canadian Amateur Championships...Was two-time all-conference choice at Eastern Michigan University...Missed the cut (71-70) at the 2010 RBC Canadian Open...Missed the cut (74-73) at the 2009 RBC Canadian Open.
tourBios.personal: Attended Grand River Collegiate school in Kitchener, Ontario, Canada...Was two-time golf MVP and inducted into the Grand River Sports Hall of Fame...Father, Charlie, owns a coffee company...Has worked in shipping and receiving in the off season...If not a professional golfer, he would be a sports journalist...Likes golf as "it allows me to set my own schedule."...First-tee introduction song would be "Can't Stop" by the Red Hot Chili Peppers...Favorite course is Royal St. Georges GC outside Toronto...Would most like to play Cypress Point...Favorite pro teams are the Carolina Panthers and Detroit Red Wings...Favorite college teams are Eastern Michigan and Michigan...Favorite TV shows are "The League" and "Workaholics."...Favorite movies are "Boondock Saints" and "Fracture"...Favorite books are The Hobbit and Guns, Germs and Steel...Favorite entertainers are Blink 182, Jimmy Eat World and Eminem...Favorite athlete is Pavel Datsyuk of the Detroit Red Wings...Favorite cities are Las Vegas and Chicago...Would like to trade places with an astronaut...Not many people know "I am unreal at Mario Kart 64."...Would like to visit Europe, purely as a tourist, not a golfer...Twitter name is @therealcamburke.
